Usage: vcpe push --manifest <path> [flags]

Pushes all service images referenced in the manifest to their registries. The registry is derived from each service's image repository. Run `podman login <registry>` before pushing to authenticated registries.

Required flags:
  --manifest <path>       Path to deployment manifest YAML

Optional flags:
  --backend <podman|docker>  Container runtime for push operations (default: podman).
  --state-root <path>     Override the default state root directory

Examples:
  vcpe push --manifest manifests/example.yaml
  vcpe push --manifest manifests/example.yaml --backend docker
